</TD><TD WIDTH="517"><FONT SIZE="2">
    Eternal Sovereign is aiming to camp the queen room in Crystal Caverns.  A group of 6 35-40 can camp this room without a lot of difficulty.  Loot dropped:-
    <UL>
    <LI>Messenger of the Queen (2h piercer 20dmg 40dly +5str/wis, PAL only)</LI>
    <LI>Crystalline Robes (Robe: AC10 +6INT +2AGI +10mana +10vs cold +5vs magic</LI>
    <LI>Glowing Velium Axe (2h slash 18dmg 37dly +5STA)</LI>
    <LI>Crystal Webshield (AC15 +20hp +20mana +10vs cold wt0.2 Priest/Caster only)</LI>
    <LI>Crystallized Swod (1h slash 11dmg 29dly)</LI>
    </UL>
    If there are a number of people 27-35 turning up, then the orcs are excellent exp and drop some VERY nice items too.  Also the orcs can be pulled fairly safely to a spot where its possible to run to the guards if you get into trouble.
    <UL>
    <LI>Herbalist pack (6 slot large bag.  25% weight reduction)</LI>
    <LI>Crystal Covered Shroud (Robe: AC12 +4str/wis/int +10vs cold)</LI>
    <LI>Blackened Crystalline Robe (AC8 +5CHA +6INT +10CR)</LI>
    <LI>Crystalline Belt (AC5 +3wis/agi +10hp)</LI>
    <LI>Foreman's Skull Cap (AC8 +4STR +2DEX +2STA +10CR wt2.0)</LI>
    </UL>
    <B>Loot Rules</B><br>
    On this raid (as on all ES Raids) loot will be given to whoever has the most use for the item.  If there are 2 or more, a /random roll will be used.  You will not be allowed to roll for the same item twice unless everyone already has the item or doesn't want it.<P>If there are any disputes, then they will be settled by the raid leader in conjunction with the Guild Officers and Guild Leader.  Their decision is final.
    
    For now, please use the bulletin board to indicate if you want to attend. Click <A href="http://bcl.icestorm.com/esguild/ubb/Forum1/HTML/000013.html">here</A> to view the thread.
